  "text": "The crown of three stars, we are guessing, indicates mastery and balancing of the mind, body, and spirit. Is this in any way correct? I am Ra. This device is astrological in origin and the interpretation given somewhat confusing. We deal, in this image, with the environment of mind. It is perhaps appropriate to release the starry crown from its stricture.",
